lead_paragraph: Liverpool roared to the top of the Premier League on Sunday, offering another dazzling demonstration of their attacking prowess under Juergen Klopp with a 6-1 demolition of Watford at an exultant Anfield.

headline.print_headline: Six-Goal Liverpool Go Top as Arsenal Miss Their Chance
